  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/007-first-light">007: First Light</a> is a May release <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/007-first-light-james-bond-preview-hitman-uncharted-comparisons">we've been playing close attention to</a> for a long time, yet we now won't get every version at once: the <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Nintendo Switch 2</a> version has been delayed.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.ppe.pl/news/406745/007-first-light-opoznione-w-jednej-wersji-informator-podaje-szczegol.html">Following insider Graczdari breaking the news</a> earlier today, the game's social media accounts <a href="https://x.com/007GameIOI/status/2041863487291294093?s=20">have confirmed</a> the delay.</p>
<p>"007 First Light comes to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC on May 27th, 2026, and Nintendo Switch 2 later this summer," the <a href="https://x.com/007GameIOI/status/2041863487291294093?s=20">007 First Light X account</a> announced. "We're excited to see players discovering James Bond's reimagined origin story, and we are looking forward to bringing you the best game experience possible across all platforms."</p>
<p><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/companies/io-interactive">IO Interactive</a>'s action-adventure game, based on the famous fictional British spy, seemed otherwise in good shape earlier this week in a new <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oti0Bofd70o">10-minute story-focused developer diary.</a></p> <figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="007 First Light - Official Path Tracing Reveal Trailer" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pzkNzkSqqic?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
